snippet.title: Tyrant's Blessing (trailer)
snippet.description:
Challenge the dread Tyrant’s undead army in this tactical turn-based fantasy game. Salvage weapons, equipment and supplies from your fallen enemies, build your team of heroes, and reclaim your homeland.


https://store.steampowered.com/app/1520760/Tyrants_Blessing/
